WEBVTT00:00:03.096 --> 00:00:04.666 align:centerCall me Ishmael.00:00:04.666 --> 00:00:08.946 align:centerSome years ago, never mind how longprecisely, having little or no money00:00:08.946 --> 00:00:13.876 align:centerin my purse, and nothing particular tointerest me on shore, I thought I would sail00:00:13.876 --> 00:00:16.266 align:centerabout a little and see thewatery part of the world.00:00:16.726 --> 00:00:20.776 align:centerIt is a way I have of driving off thespleen and regulating the circulation.00:00:21.716 --> 00:00:26.056 align:centerWhenever I find myself growing grimabout the mouth; whenever it is a damp,00:00:26.056 --> 00:00:32.466drizzly November in my soul; whenever I findmyself involuntarily pausing before coffin00:00:32.466 --> 00:00:36.116warehouses, and bringing up therear of every funeral I meet;00:00:36.116 --> 00:00:39.686and especially whenever my hyposget such an upper hand of me,00:00:39.686 --> 00:00:44.546that it requires a strong moral principleto prevent me from deliberately stepping00:00:44.546 --> 00:00:48.996into the street, and methodicallyknocking people's hats off then,00:00:48.996 --> 00:00:57.426I account it high time toget to sea as soon as I can.